Task management system

Create a new repository using https://github.com/saeloun/plate
Technical Requirements

It should be a web application.
Should be Single Page after logging in, an example of how this should look
https://monosnap.com/file/zcC2HIv9G8G1KiPtE0F8v0YRGzBEcf
It should have validations.
It should work like a single-page WEB application and should use Ajax or similar.
It should have a user authentication solution. The user should only have access to their tasks.


